data.description: Zero down eligible for qualified buyers! Beautiful home in the highly desired Woodward Hills Subdivision in Bentonville. This home features 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Spacious, open kitchen and living room with vaulted ceilings and fire place. Kitchen and bathrooms have quartz counter tops, black stainless steel appliances, and soft close cabinets & drawers. The kitchen has a nice bar area & space for your dining table. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms. For your modern connectivity needs, this house is thoughtfully designed with abundant electrical/USB outlets placed throughout. Fenced backyard. Storm shelter included! Don't miss out on this home!  $5000 in Seller Concessions!
